{"tid":980070,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"日本情歌教主西野加奈8日宣布無限期活動休止 2月初橫濱公演絕唱門票據被抬價最高70倍","createTime":"2019-01-13T08:28:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-13T09:46:38.000Z","uid":9573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a773117a122b3e46c34499750e02ee60a0a0d0b4","tid":980070,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T08:28:56.000Z","msg":"日本情歌教主西野加奈今天在官方網站宣布決定暫停演藝活動，29歲的她表示，下個月的10周年巡演告一段落後就會休息，何時復歸還沒有想好。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/01/08/realtime/5767917.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F01%2F08%2Frealtime%2F5767917.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=ad3c871a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n西野加奈今年也在「紅白歌唱大賽」出場。<br />\n<br />\n西野加奈在日本歌壇以抒情情歌稱霸女性市場，外型可愛的她也是許多女高中生的偶像。她透露自己喜歡旅行，有很多想去的地方，也有很多想做的事情。未來休息後她會進行許多挑戰，「直到回到大家面前唱歌的那天，想在生活中快樂地享受音樂。」下個月1到3日的橫濱Arena演唱會將是她最後的公演。原價580港元的門票被炒高70倍，叫價逾4萬港元一張，尾場個唱亦會在港戲院直播。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190112/large/1547292121_5ee9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190112%2Flarge%2F1547292121_5ee9.jpg&h=acbe2d4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n六合彩這晚9時15分截止投注<br />\n<br />\n西野加奈擁有多首大熱情歌，更連續9年打入《紅白歌唱大賽》，早前受訪時就透露最想去智利旅遊勝地復活節島。近日在音樂節目中演唱頗顯吃力，歌迷雖然不捨，但因為嗓子明顯不如以往，歌曲中又有許多高音，粉絲也認同她應該需要休息，養好喉嚨後再重回歌壇。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Hk2G6GqQzNE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHk2G6GqQzNE&d=QbdtIZsqsWgwJ28ExpSMKgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=468a1b7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Hk2G6GqQzNE</a><br />\n西野カナ - NO.1"},{"pid":"d45ec59d9cbd11de86d1f3887a842a841b33fb0b","tid":980070,"uid":132587,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T08:37:12.000Z","msg":"佢都算係倖田來未 中島美嘉果個梯隊之後最成功既歌姬"},{"pid":"cf839c9235258266b1e9df5f75ead94a77b61eb2","tid":980070,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T09:34:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d1502852cfaa5a9addec3f5a7216778179cacadb","tid":980070,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T09:42:47.000Z","msg":"TT<br />\n又一個歌姬唔再唱"},{"pid":"34570fe31b62e8590e3b95060ed270b70a69dffa","tid":980070,"uid":151071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf839c9235258266b1e9df5f75ead94a77b61eb2","tid":980070,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T09:34:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T09:46:38.000Z","msg":"賣曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}